# HELI

* The game is named HELI (related to helicopter or spaceship) which is a 2D space survival shooting game, where the player has to survive in the space by shooting the obstacles.

* Tools and Technology: C/C++, SDL/SDL2.

***You have to first install sdl2,sdl2_ttf and sdl2_mixer in your computer***

1) Please run the code in the terminal after going to the game folder "HELI" from the terminal:
   g++ source.cpp -w -lSDL2 -lSDL2_ttf -lSDL2_mixer && ./a.out
2) Enjoy the game.
3) See your score in the terminal after quiting the game.
4) See highscores in the highscore.txt file.

Thank you <3
